{"tid":1531263,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"202和404的約會！從製作人與練習生關係變成兄弟情：李大輝＆金敏圭同吃麻辣燙","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T12:02:53.000Z","uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0c233ce0c1b49e9af9917f6cafb5b65f3f40de1a","tid":1531263,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"202出身的愛豆和404出身的愛豆「約會」去吃麻辣燙啦~<br />\n<br />\n《Produce 101》系列第2季練習生，最後成功進組Wanna One的李大輝和《Produce 101》第4季《Produce X 101》人氣練習生金敏圭最近被拍到一同去吃麻辣燙，網民們更是給他倆的照片安上了「捕捉到李大輝、金敏圭約會現場」的標題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xsiYu10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxsiYu10.jpg&h=915975e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照片拍自首爾林蔭大道上的一家麻辣燙店，李大輝和金敏圭穿著T恤、襯衣在店裡現身，兩人都衣著休閒，沒戴帽子和口罩，反倒是同行的另一位朋友全副武裝看不到臉。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D79T3m5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD79T3m5.jpg&h=d58387a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Produce X 101》時，李大輝作為製作人造訪大本營，而金敏圭當時是練習生，兩人就這樣相熟起來，後來更是從製作人練習生的關係轉變為好兄弟，據說兩人的互稱是哥哥和弟弟。 然而李大輝和金敏圭都是2001年生，只是李大輝是「快01年生」，已經高中畢業，所以成了哥哥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HDWvk8S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHDWvk8S.jpg&h=6359e479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" 